OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FIn his official letter to the King,
OL,7,FHumza Yousaf thanked the monarch for
OL,8,Fthe "kindness" shown to himself and
OL,9,Fhis wife, ITV News Correspondent Peter
OL,10,FSmith reports
OL,12,FHumza Yousaf has officially resigned
OL,13,Fas Scotland's first minister.
OL,15,FMr Yousaf, who is the youngest and
OL,16,Ffirst person of colour to hold the top
OL,17,Fjob in Scotland, will make his final
OL,18,Fspeech to MSPs this afternoon, paving
OL,19,Fthe way for a Holyrood vote on his
OL,20,Freplacement.
