OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FIn his official letter to King
OL,7,FCharles, Mr Yousaf thanked the monarch
OL,8,Ffor the "kindness" shown to himself
OL,9,Fand his wife, Nadia El-Nakla.
OL,11,FThe Scottish government has since
OL,12,Fconfirmed Mr Yousaf's resignation has
OL,13,Fbeen accepted and the Scottish
OL,14,Fparliament has been notified.
OL,16,FHe wrote: "Throughout my time as first
OL,17,Fminister, I have been most grateful
OL,18,Ffor your counsel and the kindness you
OL,19,Fhave shown to Nadia and I.
