OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,F"It has been my pleasure to serve Your
OL,7,FMajesty and the people of Scotland
OL,8,Fsince March 2023."
OL,10,FHe announced his intention to resign
OL,11,Flast week after he ended the
OL,12,Fpowersharing deal between the SNP and
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Greens at Holyrood,
OL,14,Fcausing anger from the latter party.
OL,16,FA motion of no confidence in his
OL,17,Fleadership was put forward by the
OL,18,FScottish Tories, and with Mr Yousaf
OL,19,Funlikely to win, he stepped down from
OL,20,Fhis role and forced the SNP to find
OL,21,Fits second leader in just over a year.
