OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FMr Yousaf said he will continue to
OL,7,Fchampion the rights of the voices not
OL,8,Foften heard, including those in Gaza
OL,9,Fafter his tenure as first minister saw
OL,10,Fhim share his own personal story of
OL,11,Fhis in-laws who were trapped in the
OL,12,Fwar zone before fleeing through Egypt.
OL,14,FHe said: "Being the first minister of
OL,15,Fthe country I love, the country I am
OL,16,Fraising my family in, and the only
OL,17,Fcountry I will ever call home has been
OL,18,Fa phenomenal honour".
