OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FMr Yousaf, who at the time of his
OL,7,Fappointment was the first Muslim
OL,8,Fleader of any nation, said: "As a
OL,9,Fyoung Muslim boy, born and raised in
OL,10,FScotland, I could never have dreamt
OL,11,Fthat one day I would have the
OL,12,Fprivilege of leading my country `
OL,13,Fpeople who looked like me were not in
OL,14,Fpositions of political influence, let
OL,15,Falone leading governments when I was
OL,16,Fyounger."
