OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FAddressing the policy decisions made
OL,7,Fduring his time in office, Mr Yousaf
OL,8,Fsaid he was "proud" to have delivered
OL,9,Fa council tax freeze across Scotland
OL,10,Fand invest record amounts in the NHS.
OL,12,FHe added: "From the backbenches of the
OL,13,FScottish parliament, I will continue
OL,14,Fto champion the rights and the voices
OL,15,Fof those who are often not heard, be
OL,16,Fthey at home or abroad."
OL,18,FNew SNP leader John Swinney is to
OL,19,Fbecome Scotland's next first minister
OL,20,Fafter winning a vote at Holyrood.
