OL,3,CHumza Yousaf officially steps down as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister
OL,6,FMr Swinney won the backing of 64 MSPs,
OL,7,Fwith his nearest rival Scottish
OL,8,FConservatives leader Douglas Ross
OL,9,Fpicking up 31.
OL,11,FIt marks the second time he has served
OL,12,Fas SNP leader ` though when he held
OL,13,Fthe role previously between 2000 and
OL,14,F2004 the party was in opposition at
OL,15,FHolyrood.
